overview: 2015’s class of Playmates were a cut above the rest, and choosing the Playmate of the Year 2016 is a daunting task indeed. To help you decide, we’ve put together a compilation of our favorite shots and behind-the-scenes moments with this year’s Playmates, from January to December. Cast your vote on Playboy.com and cross your fingers that your favorite wins!.
title: Playmate Review
